203
00:11:48,610 --> 00:11:49,470
before payment.

204
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:50,030
Okay.

205
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:54,150
I've made contact with

206
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,710
