243
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:56,010
He...

244
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:57,260
Help.

245
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:01,820
[Treasures Fill the Home]

246
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:20,470
